data.description: Just starting out or down sizing? This home 5 minutes from town and all amenities is perfect for you! This ranch features a living room, kitchen, spacious dining room with extra family room space, full bath and two bedrooms all on the first floor. Upstairs you will find the third bedroom, with possible fourth bedroom or bonus office\play space! Out back enjoy a private back deck facing into the woods. Priced to sell - this home would be perfect for you! Don’t just drive by - Schedule your showing today!
